title: Moon Taxi - Cabaret (2012)
description:
Moon Taxi's 2012 album, Cabaret. Fantastic band and a phenomenal album.  I was sad to see that there weren't any decent uploads of this album, so I decided to put one up.  All songs are in MP3 format.

1. Mercury
2. All The Rage
3. Let's Go Back
4. Hypnus
5. Hideaway
6. Radio
7. Southern Trance
8. Whiskey Sunsets
9. Square Circles (feat. Matisyahu)
10. Cabaret
11. Pennies
12. Gunflower
